natgeobg - National Geographic Background
=========================================

Description
-----------
Set GNOME background to National Geographics' "Picture of the Day" using
Mojo::UserAgent.

Install
-------
natgeobg.pl depends on Mojo::UserAgent from the Mojolicious the package.
To install it run:
    cpan Mojolicious

Usage
-----
- run manually:
    perl ./natgeobg.pl

- run from CRON (every 6 hours):
    0 */6 * * *    $HOME/bin/natgeobg.pl 2>&1 > /dev/null

Bugs
----
https://github.com/arpadszasz/natgeobg/issues

